title: Carvalho (Mariano de)
body: He arrived in Funchal on December 6, 1890, and left for Lisbon on the 8th of the same month and year. He was very well received here, attending a ball at the Funchalense Club and a dinner that was offered to him in the noble hall of the former theater “D. Maria Pia“.

Mariano de Carvalho: Person who arrived in Funchal in 1890 and left for Lisbon in the same year.

1890: Person who arrived in Funchal in 1890 and left for Lisbon in the same year.
